<br>
It's not server lag.  In fact, Bazaar has to be one of the best zones in the game lag wise.  All the lag you're getting is graphic lag, your video card straining trying to draw all 400 people.  Just floor the clip plane turn off Luclin models, you'll be fine.  I'm on a 36k (modem's 56k, yah yah, but the crappy connection never breaks 38333bps) and it's just fine.<br>
<br>
Considering that it's got all the Trader info going, keeps up with all the /bazaar search requests, AND has the usual spam (moreso, in fact, since we've got everyone /oocing &quot;Where do i get traders satchels?!&quot;) , it's amazing how smooth the zone itself really is.<br>
<br>
Now if you're staring at the floor and moving like a slideshow, ya got a problem  (-8<br>
